<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>まっしろ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffe0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            background: #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .question {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        button {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #fb8c00;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>まっしろ</h1>
        <div class="question">僕のchatworkでのアイコンは？</div>
        <p>（ヒント: 僕のプロフィールに載ってるよ）</p>
        <form action="/question/massiro/answer" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="answer" required>
            <button type="submit">送信</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
